The paper discusses privacy issues related to cloud storage and proposes a distributed approach to address them. This suggests that the paper could belong to the categories of cryptography (cs.CR), databases (cs.DB), distributed computing (cs.DC), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and software engineering (cs.SE). However, since the paper primarily focuses on privacy and security concerns, cs.CR is the most likely category, followed by cs.DB and cs.DC.
